{"about_the_game":"Falsus Chronicle: Ancient Treasure is a dungeon exploring, Anime style action RPG with Roguelike elements. In this game, dungeon will randomly generate traps, monsters and loots. With our unique \u201cMonster Gem\u201d system, every different choice of classes, weapons, and skill sets effects characters raising multiple possibilities, to fulfil every single dungeon explore with funs! <br />\r\n <br />\r\nStory: <br />\r\n <br />\r\nThe story of Falsus Chronicle: Ancient Treasure takes place just 10 years after the story of Falsus Chronicle: Forgotten Child... Somewhere in Kingdom of Rista, a piece of ancient tablet was unearthed\u2026 thus the serenity between Kingdom of Rista and the nearby Rosenberg Grand Duchy was broken. Our main character, Sir Emil Adams, as a famous archaeologist and inventor, is heading for a ruin at the periphery of Kingdom of Rista for an investigation due to a commission from Rosenberg Grand Duchy. However, this \u201csimple academic investigation\u201d he thought to be has force him involve into an unpredictable storm which is hidden a deeper evil conspiracy\u2026 <br />\r\n <br />\r\nFeatures: <br />\r\n <br />\r\nDuring the explorations, Emil will encounter various enemies, players must make good use of the Monster Gems, which are looted from the beaten monsters, to boost character abilities, infuse battle buffs, even upgrade certain skills. No matter you are a player prefers physical attack, magical attack, high critical chance or an atypical melee wizard styles, you can always shape a style according to your preference. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 A roguelite &amp; dungeon exploring game, random generate maps, traps, loots and enemies. Every single entry to a dungeon, it\u2019s a whole new adventure!<br />\r\n\u2022 Cute characters and delicate dungeon scenes. <br />\r\n\u2022 Companions with different traits; multiple weapon types; unique skills! <br />\r\n\u2022 Skill sets determined by character classes and equipped weapon. <br />\r\n\u2022 \u201cMonster Gem\u201d reinforcement system, shapes characters with different ability strengths and combat styles. <br />\r\n\u2022 Various side quests and rewards.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"CHAPTER 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/332aee5a99957eaa08f7d54ce805e848c83ac5fb.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/9c493c5c0d363c25fa1986a97a3908085eab75ea.jpg"},{"name":"Trials Stage 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/233aa4507419df44e5908463edf29f0aba94ba6c.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/fd51c488fbf712597bf415ad651585f28653ebb1.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/2b2e85df30fbebd216d36f370253a367e7aaa214.jpg"},{"name":"Trials Stage 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/765cf826e3800de1d48ac42df9ab5cfa16ccfcee.jpg"},{"name":"Trials Stage 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/48b0242a87822cb20de637f7ab4ba0b1a587a128.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/a47f122c50a62a40444cd435a873edf6450af215.jpg"},{"name":"Gem of insanity price , Businessman of suspicious","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/745930/3f2548fc20133d782cb4bb8caa0983c4c7e24424.jpg"}],"total":9},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1529477645","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745930/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1529477645","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745930/c